Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only fulfilled your duty as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat the sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please, get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... please save as many lives as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me who brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me who brought that monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are several blood vessels embedded in this A.V.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.81,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Note:  A.V.M. = Arteriovenous Malformation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut all the influx arteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with all the outflowing arteries afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished the extraction of the nidus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That went very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clipping went very quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a marvelous operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that was your first operation \N since your sabbatical...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your genius has only grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:37.48,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,315)\fad(417,134)}Pursued
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is amazing, Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The news wasn't about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is because you performed a perfect surgery \N with my father's team last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure my father appreciates your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are responsible for improving the hospital's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be thankful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since it is thanks to your father that \N I can work like this in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kenzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive everything will work out fine \N if you follow in my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is only a matter of time before my \N father becomes the chief director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll soon be the head of the surgical department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, a director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will make me the wife of a director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better make me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because hardship doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The madam is resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take up a lot of her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But please, come back after you have \N made an appointment to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a policeman here to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Policeman...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Ms. Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was investigating your father's death nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go, Horst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that worthless detective who couldn't solve a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something to have \N maintained this large mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even after the death of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... if anything, the furnishings have \N become even more extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see how much I've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from my father's inheritance and the alimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see something you like, you are \N welcome to take it home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have my alcohol, that is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall seeing it anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since it is an item from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a simple pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if you look closely, the weaving is very elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rather high quality tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This tie gave me a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since it was made nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, however, this item...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a limited edition, made specially \N for frequent clients of the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on their list of clients...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I found your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bought this as a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be an important key to solving a certain murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought presents for so many men that I don't \N have time to remember every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the men chasing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are only after my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one was a gold digger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is not a single human being who would \N love me from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I robbed them all with divorce settlements!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will cost you big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact me if you remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a  bottle of whiskey the next time you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva, can't you say something to your father about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only performed the operation in the \N order the patients were brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... the engagement ring I gave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that suit looks spectacular, Dr. Norden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look rather dazzling tonight yourself, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horst!  Get the car ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have gotten better, Mr. Hess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you might be able to \N leave the hospital this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's wedding is next month.  \N Do you think I'll be able to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please take it easy at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is all because you tried your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you as my doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel like I'll see not only my daughter's wedding, \N but my grandchild's wedding as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a wonderful doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue your work at this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to visit my other patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be busy, so can you tell him to come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Kenzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things happened between us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asleep already, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard, but pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you took a sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you should take a rest like that from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the rumors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Springtime, ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we used to go driving a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to go swimming in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got scared and stopped you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally realized after ruining three different marriages...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who really loved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was you, Kenzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you feel that way about me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police came asking about your necktie, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did something bad with that tie, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That necktie was definitely the \N one I gave you as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay quiet as long as you do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the police about the necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them that the incident where my \N father and the others were killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was all your fault too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Dr. Tenma to me as a material witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this isn't enough evidence to tie him to \N the murders of the Fortners and Mr. Mauler...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only concerned with the murder that took \N place at Heidelberg Castle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to solve a number of cases at once now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resignation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me for my selfishness, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been a lot of strange rumors \N about you recently, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't believe any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you think this over and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is suspected of murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close off all entrances to the ward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the rear entrances as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is obstruction of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way Dr. Tenma would kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved all our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there is a huge commotion over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of police cars out there, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please drop me off in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are busy as usual, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an operation waiting  for me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an attitude problem, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not a doctor!  You are just in it for the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like him... People like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find the twins anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... happened here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably already forgot about those two little twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have died back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you brought me back to life, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:45.32,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,286)\fad(384,117)}5 Months Later
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is gonna be another hot day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hot, dressed like that in the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?  Is that newspaper three days old?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said another middle aged couple \N was murdered, this time in Verden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said a doctor did it, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you said you were \N going to Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know someone there or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll meet him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have to go.
